From 819d5aa7ea1a21e95763b29b200863851048a9af Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Developer <dev@example.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 10:05:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add per-item customisation notes before adding to cart

- AppContext: cart shape updated from {[id]: qty} to {[id]: {quantity, note}};
  addToCart/replaceCart accept an optional note param; placeOrder sends note
  to backend per item

- ItemDetailScreen: inline TextInput (150 char limit) between qty row and
  footer CTA; note passed to addToCart on confirm

- RestaurantScreen: Add button now opens a bottom-sheet Modal so the customer
  can type a note before the item enters the cart; saved note shown inline
  under the dish price in the menu list

- CartScreen: note rendered under each cart row price so customers can review
  customisations before placing the order
